ment under a </span><a style=""line-height: 14pt;"" target=""_blank"" href=""http://oikeusministerio.fi/en/index/currentissues/tiedotteet/2012/01/kansalaisaloitekayttoonmaaliskuunalusta.html"">2012 reform</a><span style=""line-height: 14pt;""> to the Finnish Constitution. </span></p>",1,"2014-10-17 11:00:11",FI,ipr,"initiative, finland, crowdsourced-copyright-reform",government
