-image-source: initial; border-image-width: initial; font-stretch: inherit;"">physical</span></span></span>&nbsp;public places&nbsp;<span class=""ins""><span style=""border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm;""><span style=""border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-source: initial; border-image-width: initial; font-stretch: inherit;"">should always be subject to prior authorisation from the authors or any proxy acting for them</span></span></span></span></i><span class=""ins""><span style=""background: white; border: none windowtext 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: none windowtext 0cm; padding: 0cm;""><span style=""border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-source: initial; border-image-width: initial; font-stretch: inherit;"">"".</span></span></span></span></p>",1,"2015-06-26 15:20:03",EU,ipr,"infosoc-directive, european-parliament, legal-committee, vote, ammendments, report, julia-reda, copyright-reform, freedom-of-panorama",european-bodies
